      "updatedAt": 1780271480178,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Subagents only report back to the lead and\nCANNOT talk to each other. Agent teams are\nPEERS with a mailbox (SendMessage) + a shared\ntask list — that is what enables real collaboration.",
      "fontSize": 13,
